  "title": "[Official] Epic x ParCool",
  "description": "An official add-on for Epic Fight and ParCool! compatibility  presented by Epic Fight team",
  "body": "![Logo](https://i.imgur.com/a1wrxrK.png)\n\n_**Epic Fight** has an advanced animation library, and **Parcool!** has dynamic player movements that interact with terrain. What will happen if these creative works meet in the Minecraft world…?_\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/CWsUfxt.jpg)\n\n<details>\n<summary>Animations</summary>\n\n<div class=\"spoiler\"><p>First, you gotta enable <strong>Battle mode</strong> to activate <strong>Epic Fight-based animations</strong> (default switching key is R)</p><h4><strong>ParCool original movements</strong></h4><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Fast run</p><p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/pcD9Nql.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"200\" height=\"225\"></p><p>Cat leap</p><p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/p02y9o2.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"201\" height=\"226\"></p><p>Roll</p><p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/2iclAMJ.gif\" width=\"199\" height=\"178\"></p><p>Wall grab &amp; Wall climb</p><p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/tN8ZuxC.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"201\" height=\"208\"></p><p>Vault</p><p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/2qE05UQ.gif\" width=\"204\" height=\"237\"></p><p>Dive &amp; Skydive</p><p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/3hL1NyX.gif\" width=\"205\" height=\"235\"></p><p><em>Find out more animations in game!</em></p><h4><strong>ParCool-based, but unique movements (only work in Battle mode)</strong></h4><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Chain movement</p><p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/DgW7RVu.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"212\" height=\"289\"></p><p>Wall movement</p><p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/qAVatkM.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"213\" height=\"198\"></p></div>\n\n</details>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/CWsUfxt.jpg\" alt=\"Bold Breakline1\" width=\"1344\" height=\"48\" /></p></p></p></p>\n\n<h2><center><font color=yellow><strong><em>Support &amp; Affiliates</em></strong></font></center></h2>\n\n<center><a href=\"https://sparkedhost.com/\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/kTgYcrh.pnghttps://i.imgur.com/kTgYcrh.png\" alt=\"Modloader\"></a></center>\n\n<br>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/CWsUfxt.jpg\" alt=\"Bold Breakline1\" width=\"1344\" height=\"48\" /></p>\n\n<center><a title=\"Patreon\" href=\"https://www.patreon.com/bePatron?u=53051224\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://github.com/Yesssssman/epicfightmod/assets/77132244/7c517b51-581a-48dc-9130-aaad326dbcb4\" alt=\"Patreon\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a>&nbsp; &nbsp;<a title=\"Discord\" href=\"https://discord.com/invite/NbAJwj8RHg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://github.com/Yesssssman/epicfightmod/assets/77132244/f3358cb9-f3cd-46e7-9ed0-a90bc2b1b188\" alt=\"Discord\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a>&nbsp; &nbsp;<a title=\"YouTube\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/@yesman4100\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://github.com/Yesssssman/epicfightmod/assets/77132244/3f2de855-e926-4eb9-a20c-4c6f44828250\" alt=\"Youtube\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a>&nbsp; &nbsp;<a href=\"https://epicfight-docs.readthedocs.io/en/latest/\"><img src=\"https://github.com/Yesssssman/epicfightmod/assets/77132244/23220c47-c1e5-4e2b-82aa-876a86d7ed1a\" alt=\"GitHub\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a></center>\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>",
